info.name: Paneer Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Soft yet perferctly grilled Paneer patties are paired with fresh cucumber, tomato and onion and topped with a delicious mayo inside a warm bun.  Every bite has a balanced all-in-one flavour.(640 Calories)

info.name: Classic Veg Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | A delicious veg patty seared on the outside but juicy on the inside dressed with a silky smooth mayo, fresh veggies and wrapped with a soft bun. Ideal for a noon lunch or party dinner.(420 Calories)

info.name: Veg Chipotle Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | You could eat several of these in one sitting! Smoky chipotle mayo smothered onto a perfeclty grilled veg patty along with slices of juicy tomato, cucumber & onion! What's not to love about it! (520 Calories)

info.name: The Spicy Veg Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Trust us, this burger pairs beautifully with a chilled drink! Moist & juicy veg patty and fresh veggies are topped with spicy schezwan mayo giving it the perfect finish inside the softest bun. (450 Calories)

info.name: Mexican Wave Paneer Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Delicious Paneer patty is topped with a perfect portion of equally delicious chipotle mayo and slices of veggies and fresh green lettuce. A burger that lives up to its name! (640 Calories)

info.name: Five Spice Paneer Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | A special Paneer patty grilled till its crisp yet juicy and then placed on a soft bun with fresh veggies and smeared with a generous helping of spicy shezwan mayo to bring it all together! (570 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | A mouthwatering juicy chicken patty stacked with fresh tomato, cucumber, onion and lettuce. All tied together with our delicious signature mayonnaise. A classic always remains a classic! (440 Calories)

info.name: Lamb Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | An all time favourite among burger fans. A juicy patty made with the best lamb and flavoured so well that it blends perfectly with fresh veggies and a delicious mayonnaise. Simple yet flavoursome! (360 Calories)

info.name: Egg and Cheese Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | The combination of egg and cheese inside a warm bun with slices of juicy tomato, fresh cucumber, green lettuce and onion makes this a light guilt-free burger, just right for a midday snack! (500 Calories)

info.name: Mexican Fried Chicken Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | A grilled chicken patty with juicy tomato, cucumber, onion and plenty of deliciously smokey chipotle sauce and a bun that soaks it all up. Its too good to be missed! (550 Calories)

info.name: Schezwan Chicken Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Delicious burger bursting with flavour in every bite! A crispy chicken patty inside a soft fresh bun with veggies and a spicy schezwan mayo make this a must-have at every party! (530 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Premium Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Fresh warm bun, juicy tomato, fresh cucumber, crisp lettuce and our smooth signature mayonnaise - all with that insanely delicious Special Chicken Patty. It doesn't get better than this! (440 Calories)

info.name: Los Pos Hermanos Chicken Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | A chicken burger with a flavoursome twist! A scrumptious chicken patty served in a soft bun along with fresh vegetables and our in-house smokey spicy chipotle mayo. A hearty meal to end the day! (490 Calories)

info.name: Schezwan Chicken Premium Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | The ultimate premium burger with flavours that compliment each other so well! A premium chicken burger patty with fresh veggies and a perfectly spiced schezwan mayo that wraps it all together! (410 Calories)

info.name: Chipotle Lamb Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | An appetizing burger that can be had as a meal by itself or a snack! The perfect pairing of a scrumptious lamb patty with chipotle mayonnaise & fresh veggies brings in a harmony of flavours. (530 Calories)

info.name: The Unforgiving Mutton Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | A supremely delicious lamb patty is stacked with tomato, cucumber, lettuce, onion and a knockout schezwan mayo to give it that extra kick. One bite of this juicy burger will have you asking for more! (490 Calories)

info.name: Bannur Lamb Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Succulent juicy lamb patty seared to perfection & fresh veggies packed inside a soft warm bun topped with our signature mayonnaise make this flavoursome burger a must-have for any meal. (360 Calories)

info.name: Juicy Lamb Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Irresistible & tender lamb patty is packed inside a fresh bun with juicy and crisp vegetables and smothered with a generous helping of the best chipotle mayo. You cannot miss this one! (290 Calories)

info.name: Schezwan Premium Lamb Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | This burger is perfect for game night with friends! Our inhouse spicy schezwan mayonnaise blends perfectly with a succulent lamb patty, fresh tomato, cucumber & onion inside a warm bun. (290 Calories)

info.name: Classic Veg Beast Burger
info.description: Serves 1 | Veggies never tasted so delicious! Three perfectly seared veg patties placed on fresh and crunchy tomato, cucumber, lettuce and onion with a generous dollop of mayo make this an awesome beast burger! (830 Calories)

info.name: Veg Moburg
info.description: Serves 1 | A unique burger of a soft bun layered with delicious veg fried momos and fresh vegetables, all tied together with our signature sauce. (360 Calories)

info.name: Corn & Cheese Moburg
info.description: Serves 1 | Delightful parcels of happiness packed with cheese, crunchy corn, fried to perfection and layered inside a burger bun. Enjoy as an anytime snack or a meal by itself. (370 Calories)

info.name: Paneer Moburg
info.description: Serves 1 | Momos stuffed with a delicious filling of minced paneer are fried and placed inside a burger bun with crunchy fresh vegetables. (360 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Moburg
info.description: Serves 1 | Most popular street food of delicious fried chicken momos layered inside a burger bun with fresh veggies. (390 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Cheese Moburg
info.description: Serves 1 | These piping hot fried momos are filled with delicious chicken & gooey cheese and placed inside a soft bun along with crunchy vegetables. Great party snack for the weekend. (390 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Tikka Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | Boneless chunks of chicken marinated with spices and cooked till tender is topped over white rice, a crunchy fresh salad and thick delicious gravy. Scrumptious meal for any day of the week. (800 Calories)

info.name: Mixed Veg Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | A steamy hot bowl of rice compliments well with the goodness of mixed vegetables and a thick gravy that tops it off. A perfect bowl of health and taste! (770 Calories)

info.name: Chilli Paneer Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfect harmony of soft Paneer tossed in the right spices and served with aromatic rice, freshly chopped veggies and a delicious thick gravy to add to the flavour. (790 Calories)

info.name: Paneer Tikka Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | A truly satisfying meal of rice, freshly cut vegetable salad and well marinated paneer that is grilled till crisp on the outside yet soft inside. Just what perfect dinners are made of. (780 Calories)

info.name: Egg Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | A light meal perfect for every night of the week. Rice topped with crunchy and fresh vegetables and healthy egg. Flavour and health in a bowl. (780 Calories)

info.name: Bhuna Chicken Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | Rice and veggies pair with chicken that is tossed in a spicy mix and then cooked in its own juices till perfectly dry yet full of flavour. Top the rice with the gravy and complete your meal! (790 Calories)

info.name: Szechuan Chicken Rice Bowl
info.description: Serves 1 | A meal of rice and garden fresh veggies with the goodness of Schezuan Chicken made with the right balance of spices. A delicious weekend dinner to enjoy with friends and family. (780 Calories)

info.name: French Fries
info.description: Serves 1 | Be it a side dish to a meal or just a snack, these crisp fried French Fries are so satisfying! (440 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Popcorn
info.description: Serves 1 | Crispy, golden fried chicken bits perfect as anytime snacks. (470 Calories)

info.name: Jalepeno Poppers
info.description: Serves 1 | Lightly spiced, lightly coated and fried to perfection, these round pops will make everyone love the wholesome flavour of garlic! (470 Calories)

info.name: Chicken Fingers
info.description: Serves 1 | A crunchy, mouth-watering appetizer of spicy, batter-fried chicken fingers. (340 Calories)

info.name: Veg Fingers
info.description: Serves 1 | Long pieces of crumb coated veg fingers that are a great accompaniment to a Kaati roll! (400 Calories)

info.name: Peri Peri French Fries
info.description: Serves 1 | Humble fries that are fried to a crisp and spiced with the zingy flavour of Peri Peri. These are sure to turn the heat on! (450 Calories)

info.name: Lemon Pepper French Fries
info.description: Serves 1 | A unique seasoning of lemony tang with freshly ground pepper dusted on top of crispy fried french fries. Worthy of the finger lick! (440 Calories)

info.name: Chilli Garlic French Fries
info.description: Serves 1 | French fries sprinkled generously with our in-house punchy seasoning of Chilli Garlic. Warning - these get over in a jiffy! (440 Calories)

info.name: Choco Lava Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A small chocolate cake with a soft, gooey center of rich chocolate. This cake is best enjoyed warm with a scoop of vanilla ice cream, creating a perfect balance of rich chocolate and creamy sweetness.

info.name: Walnut Brownie
info.description: Serves 1 | A dense & moist pastry that combines a rich, chocolatey flavor with the nutty crunch of walnut and baked until it has a crispy top and a fudgy center. It is an indulgent treat for chocolate lovers.

info.name: Chocolate Truffle Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A luxious chocolate sponge mixed with our chocolate ganache and filled to the brim in our jars, cant get more sinful than this. (440 Calories)

info.name: Red Velvet Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A new way to enjoy our Red Velvet Cake! This jar has Red Velvet cake layered with silken whipped cream and a topping of Red Velvet crumbs. A perfect dessert to gift to friends or eat by yourself! (140 Calories)

info.name: Death By Chocolate (DBC) Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Insanely delicious jar for those who love indulging in chocolate! A fudge-like cake & chocolate Mousse cream topped with a layer of chocolate shavings. (290 Calories)

info.name: Black Forest Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic chocolate sponge cake, freshly whipped cream topped with cherries and chocolate shavings giving the jar its rightful glory. (330 Calories)

info.name: Chocolate Milkshake
info.description: Serves 1 | This baby doesn't need to be described. You all know you crave this everyday! (330 Calories)

info.name: Rose Milkshake
info.description: Serves 1 | We bring you the vintage rose milkshake which will bring back all the beautiful childhood memories you made while drinking it. (360 Calories)

info.name: Red Velvet Thick Shake
info.description: Serves 1 | An indulgent shake that looks just as pretty as it tastes. A blend of Red Velvet pastry with Vanilla ice cream makes this such an irresistible shake perfect to share with your loved one. (430 Calories)

info.name: Brownie Thick Shake
info.description: Serves 1 | A blend of chocolate brownie with milk and smooth Vanilla ice cream. Just the right hint of chocolate and vanilla in a bottle. (720 Calories)

info.name: Butterscotch Milkshake
info.description: Serves 1 | For all those Butterscotch lovers, what else can quench your cravings better than a butterscotch milkshake. (360 Calories)

info.name: Chocolate Truffle Thick Shake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dessert so creamy & delicious. The perfect blend of Chocolate Truffle pastry with ice cream. Dessert perfection in a bottle. (620 Calories)
